snippet.title: Call of Duty: Warzone Mobile - Pre-register Now
snippet.description:
Get ready to drop in from wherever life takes you with classic #Warzone features, 120 live players, and the return of the classic BR map Verdansk! #WarzoneMobile is a world-class MOBILE-first experience, down to its core. Pre-register now: https://bit.ly/WarzoneMobileSignUpNow

Follow us for all the latest intel:
Facebook: https://facebook.com/CODWarzoneMobile/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WarzoneMobile
Instagram: https://instagram.com/codwarzonemobile/
